msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/name"
msgid "Goodwood"
msgstr "Goodwood"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/name_big"
msgid "Goodwood"
msgstr "Goodwood"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/story"
msgid ""
"Operation Goodwood starts today.\n"
"\n"
"More than one thousand RAF heavy bombers, flying extremely low, are on their "
"way to bomb enemy positions in Colombelles, Cagny, and a number of other "
"villages and towns.\n"
"\n"
"Thanks to the air and artillery support, progress has been good so far; "
"you’re already miles to the south of Caen. In front lies your target for "
"today, which is the village of Cagny.\n"
"\n"
"We have no idea what the bombing attacks have achieved, or what remains of "
"the enemy; the whole area in and around the village looks like it has been "
"completely obliterated. Take control of the area and form a closed front to "
"defend against any possible German counterattacks."
msgstr ""
"La operación Goodwood comienza hoy.\n"
"\n"
"Más de mil bombarderos pesados de la RAF, volando a muy baja altura, se "
"dirigen a bombardear posiciones enemigas en Colombelles, Cagny y otras "
"aldeas y pueblos.\n"
"\n"
" Gracias al apoyo aéreo y de artillería, hasta ahora se ha avanzado bien; ya "
"estás a kilómetros al sur de Caen. Delante se encuentra tu objetivo de hoy, "
"que es la aldea de Cagny.\n"
"\n"
"No tenemos ni idea de qué han conseguido los bombardeos, ni de qué queda del "
"enemigo; toda la zona del pueblo y sus alrededores parece haber sido "
"completamente arrasada. Toma el control de la zona y forma un frente cerrado "
"para defenderos de cualquier posible contraataque alemán."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/date"
msgid "July 18th, 1944 · South-East of Caen, Normandy"
msgstr "18 de julio de 1944 · Sureste de Caen, Normandía"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/place"
msgid "2nd Armoured battalion, Irish Guards"
msgstr "2.º Batallón Blindado, Guardia Irlandesa"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Any planned German counterthrust has been stopped dead in its tracks, even "
"if our losses now prevent us from going on an all- out offensive. Have a "
"rest, you deserve it."
msgstr ""
"Cualquier contraataque alemán que se hubiera planeado ha quedado totalmente "
"frustrado, aunque nuestras pérdidas nos impidan ahora lanzar una ofensiva "
"total. Descansa, te lo mereces."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This makes us look like useless bleeders! Instead of a splendid victory "
"we’ve been routed like never before. The Germans will keep their hold on "
"Normandy and we’re stuck in the middle of nowhere. Try again!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto nos hace parecer unos inútiles! En lugar de una espléndida victoria, "
"hemos sufrido una derrota como nunca antes. Los alemanes mantendrán su "
"control sobre Normandía y nosotros nos quedaremos atrapados en medio de la "
"nada. ¡Inténtalo de nuevo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/mission_option_select1"
msgid ""
"Select your Doctrine for the mission.\n"
"It affects available units list and objectives.       "
msgstr ""
"Selecciona tu doctrina para la misión. Afecta a la lista de unidades "
"disponibles y a los objetivos. "

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/doctrine_allround"
msgid "All-Round: Churchill AVRE + Achilles Mk. II"
msgstr "Versátil: Churchill AVRE + Achilles Mk. II"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/doctrine_defensive"
msgid "Defensive: Cromwell Mk. VI CS + Staghound AA"
msgstr "Defensivo: Cromwell Mk. VI CS + Staghound AA"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/doctrine_irregular"
msgid "Irregular: Sherman “Crab” + Churchill Mk.VIII"
msgstr "Irregular: Sherman «Crab» + Churchill Mk.VIII"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/doctrine_offensive"
msgid "Offensive: Churchill “Crocodile” + BL 5.5-inch Mk.III"
msgstr "Ofensiva: Churchill «Crocodile» + BL 5,5 pulgadas Mk.III"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/cutscene/intro_01"
msgid ""
"Battalion, listen up! Today we have to secure the town of Cagny and provide "
"cover to assaulting mechanized convoys."
msgstr ""
"¡Batallón, atención! Hoy tenemos que asegurar la ciudad de Cagny y "
"proporcionar cobertura a los convoyes mecanizados de asalto."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/cutscene/intro_02"
msgid "Don’t worry about Jerry, the RAF has served them bombs for breakfast."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes por Jerry, la RAF les ha servido bombas para desayunar."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/cutscene/intro_03"
msgid "Ambush! Multiple AT guns!"
msgstr "¡Emboscada! ¡Varias armas antitanque!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/cutscene/intro_04"
msgid "Where the hell did they come from?!"
msgstr "¿De dónde demonios han salido?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part01_01"
msgid ""
"Second wave, move out and eliminate the enemy! Remember, every phase in this "
"operation is scheduled for a specific time."
msgstr ""
"Segunda oleada, ¡salid y eliminad al enemigo! Recordad que cada fase de esta "
"operación está programada para una hora específica."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part01_02"
msgid ""
"That’s a damn bloodbath! We shouldn’t attack them in the open. This part "
"looks like the weakest spot in the German line. We’ll have higher chances to "
"break through there."
msgstr ""
"¡Eso es una auténtica carnicería! No deberíamos atacarlos en campo abierto. "
"Esta parte parece el punto más débil de la línea alemana. Tendremos más "
"posibilidades de abrirnos paso por ahí."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part01_03"
msgid ""
"The AT guns on the right flank control the main road. If we destroy them, "
"we’ll be able to request additional units."
msgstr ""
"Los cañones antitanque del flanco derecho controlan la carretera principal. "
"Si los destruimos, podremos solicitar unidades adicionales."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part01_04"
msgid "Good, we can call in reinforcements now."
msgstr "Bien, ya podemos pedir refuerzos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part01_05"
msgid ""
"Sergeant O’Hara, I need you to assist the other vehicles. Move to the left "
"and destroy the remaining guns!"
msgstr ""
"Sargento O'Hara, necesito que ayudes a los otros vehículos. ¡Muévete hacia "
"la izquierda y destruye las armas restantes!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part01_06"
msgid ""
"Where the hell did they get these AT guns from? The carpet bombing should "
"have wiped them out! Never mind. We are already behind schedule, so let’s "
"move on."
msgstr ""
"¿De dónde demonios han sacado estas armas antitanque? ¡El bombardeo "
"intensivo debería haberlas destruido! No importa. Ya vamos con retraso, así "
"que sigamos adelante."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/"
"part01_gun_destroyed_01"
msgid "That son of a bitch is down!"
msgstr "¡Ese hijo de puta está en el suelo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/"
"part01_gun_destroyed_02"
msgid "Nice hit, the bastards are dead!"
msgstr "¡Buen impacto, los cabrones están muertos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_01"
msgid ""
"Jerry is retreating to the north and digging in, which will slow down our "
"offensive. Get rid of them as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"Jerry se está retirando hacia el norte y atrincherando, lo que ralentizará "
"nuestra ofensiva. Elimínalos lo antes posible."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_02_allround"
msgid ""
"The Germans have turned the entire road into a stronghold. Shit, the house-"
"to-house clearing is gonna take the whole day…"
msgstr ""
"Los alemanes han convertido toda la carretera en una fortaleza. Mierda, el "
"registro casa por casa va a llevar todo el día..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_03_allround"
msgid ""
"Lucky for us, we can turn these houses into their graves. Gentlemen, I would "
"like to introduce our demolition miracle - Churchill AVRE. Its firepower is "
"enough to get rid of entire fortifications in the space of a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"Por suerte para nosotros, podemos convertir estas casas en sus tumbas. "
"Caballeros, me gustaría presentarles nuestro milagro de la demolición: el "
"Churchill AVRE. Su potencia de fuego es suficiente para acabar con "
"fortificaciones enteras en cuestión de minutos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_04_allround"
msgid "The AVRE has arrived. Now show Jerry there is nowhere to hide!"
msgstr ""
"El AVRE ha llegado. ¡Ahora demuéstrale a Jerry que no hay ningún lugar donde "
"esconderse!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_05_allround"
msgid ""
"This 230mm beast is really wild. Good work men, this road is no longer a "
"threat to us."
msgstr ""
"Esta bestia de 230 mm es una locura. Buen trabajo, chicos, esta carretera ya "
"no es una amenaza para nosotros."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_02_offensive"
msgid ""
"The Germans have dug trenches between these hedgerows and everywhere else. "
"Shit, this clearing is gonna take the whole day…"
msgstr ""
"Los alemanes han cavado trincheras entre estos setos y por todas partes. "
"Mierda, limpiar esto va a llevar todo el día..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_03_offensive"
msgid ""
"Lucky for us, we can literally smoke them out. Gentlemen, I would like to "
"introduce a solution against these rats - the Churchill Crocodile. And "
"what’s better than a flamethrower? That’s right! A bloody armoured "
"flamethrower!"
msgstr ""
"Por suerte para nosotros, podemos ahuyentarlos literalmente con humo. "
"Señores, me gustaría presentarles una solución contra estas ratas: el "
"Churchill Crocodile. ¿Y qué hay mejor que un lanzallamas? ¡Exacto! ¡Un "
"lanzallamas blindado!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_04_offensive"
msgid ""
"The Crocodile has arrived. Now make Jerry regret he survived the carpet "
"bombing!"
msgstr ""
"El Crocodile ha llegado. ¡Ahora haz que los boches se arrepientan de haber "
"sobrevivido al bombardeo intenso!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_05_offensive"
msgid ""
"Smoking them out is definitely easier than clearing every German foxhole in "
"the area. Good work, men."
msgstr ""
"Sacarlos de ahí es sin duda más fácil que limpiar todas las trincheras "
"alemanas de la zona. Buen trabajo, chicos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_02_defensive"
msgid ""
"The Germans have even more guns! Shit, we’re gonna lose so many tanks again…"
msgstr ""
"¡Los alemanes tienen aún más cañones! Mierda, vamos a perder tantos tanques "
"otra vez..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_03_defensive"
msgid ""
"Lucky for us, we finally received support against AT guns. Gentlemen, I "
"would like to introduce the Cromwell VI. Its mobility and 95mm gun allows it "
"to manoeuvre in close quarters and avoid the enemy's field of view."
msgstr ""
"Por suerte para nosotros, por fin hemos recibido apoyo contra los cañones "
"antitanque. Señores, me gustaría presentarles el Cromwell VI. Su movilidad y "
"su cañón de 95 mm le permiten maniobrar en espacios reducidos y evitar el "
"campo de visión del enemigo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_04_defensive"
msgid ""
"The Cromwell has arrived. Just provide it with precise coordinates and it "
"will take care of the rest."
msgstr ""
"El Cromwell ha llegado. Solo tienes que proporcionarle las coordenadas "
"precisas y él se encargará del resto."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_05_defensive"
msgid ""
"Where was this Cromwell when we were attacking the first line? Could’ve "
"saved so many lives…"
msgstr ""
"¿Dónde estaba este Cromwell cuando atacábamos la primera línea? Podría haber "
"salvado tantas vidas..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_02_irregular"
msgid ""
"The Germans have set up an entire minefield close to their positions! Shit, "
"we’re gonna waste the whole day waiting for engineers…"
msgstr ""
"¡Los alemanes han colocado todo un campo de minas cerca de vuestras "
"posiciones! Mierda, vamos a perder todo el día esperando a los zapadores..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_03_irregular"
msgid ""
"Lucky for us, we have a reliable sapper. Gentlemen, I would like to "
"introduce a solution against all minefields - the Sherman Crab. Use it for "
"clearing up the mines."
msgstr ""
"Por suerte para nosotros, contamos con un zapador de confianza. Señores, me "
"gustaría presentarles una solución contra todos los campos minados: el "
"Sherman Crab. Úsenlo para limpiar las minas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_04_irregular"
msgid "The Crab has arrived. Now get rid of this minefield."
msgstr "El Crab ha llegado. Ahora limpia este campo minado."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_05_irregular"
msgid "Perfect, these mines are no danger to us anymore. Good work, men."
msgstr ""
"Perfecto, estas minas ya no suponen ningún peligro para nosotros. Buen "
"trabajo, chicos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_06"
msgid ""
"Deal with the remaining Germans in the northern part of town so we can "
"advance further."
msgstr ""
"Acaba con los alemanes que quedan en la parte norte de la ciudad para que "
"podamos seguir avanzando."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_07"
msgid "Excellent, the northern town is ours."
msgstr "Excelente, la ciudad del norte es nuestra."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_08"
msgid "And here is the air force. The most useless unit of today…"
msgstr "Y aquí está la fuerza aérea. La unidad más inútil de hoy en día..."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_09"
msgid ""
"Don’t jump to conclusions. One of these planes is going in circles, he is "
"probably scouting the area. Let’s see what enemy units he can spot."
msgstr ""
"No saques conclusiones precipitadas. Uno de estos aviones está volando en "
"círculos, probablemente esté explorando la zona. Veamos qué unidades "
"enemigas puede detectar."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_10"
msgid ""
"Lots of Germans with anti-tank equipment are waiting for us. O’Hara, mark "
"their positions so we know where exactly to expect more of these ambushes."
msgstr ""
"Muchos alemanes con equipo antitanque os están esperando. O'Hara, marca sus "
"posiciones para que sepamos exactamente dónde esperar más emboscadas de este "
"tipo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part02_doc_unit_lost"
msgid "Damn, they’ve destroyed our special vehicle!"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea, han destruido vuestro vehículo especial!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_01"
msgid ""
"We are almost at the finish line. There are still some remaining German "
"forces up ahead. I am providing you with more reinforcements so you can "
"crush them."
msgstr ""
"Estamos casi en la meta. Todavía quedan algunas fuerzas alemanas por "
"delante. Te estoy proporcionando más refuerzos para que puedas aplastarlos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_02"
msgid ""
"The squadron we saw before reports movement of an armoured column moving in "
"our direction. Be prepared for potential counter-attacks."
msgstr ""
"La escuadra que vimos antes informa del movimiento de una columna blindada "
"que se dirige hacia nosotros. Estad preparados para posibles contraataques."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_03"
msgid "Enemy armoured vehicles to the south!"
msgstr "¡Vehículos blindados enemigos al sur!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_04"
msgid ""
"They are sending small anti-tank groups! Keep infantry close to our tanks to "
"cover them."
msgstr ""
"¡Están enviando pequeños grupos antitanque! Mantén a la infantería cerca de "
"nuestros tanques para protegerlos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_05"
msgid "Incoming artillery! Take cover!"
msgstr "¡Artillería entrante! ¡Ponte a cubierto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_06"
msgid ""
"The artillery is very accurate, meaning someone is spotting for their "
"battery. O'Hara, find this observer and deal with him!"
msgstr ""
"La artillería es muy precisa, lo que significa que alguien está localizando "
"vuestra batería. ¡O'Hara, encuentra a ese observador y ocúpate de él!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_07"
msgid "Got that damn observer! This artillery should not fire anymore."
msgstr ""
"¡Tenemos a ese maldito observador! Esta artillería no debería disparar más."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_08"
msgid ""
"Shit, that artillery observer got away! Don’t be surprised if there are "
"further artillery strikes."
msgstr ""
"¡Mierda, el observador de artillería se ha escapado! No te sorprendas si hay "
"más ataques de artillería."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_09"
msgid "What the hell is that?! Has anyone seen these tanks before?"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios es eso? ¿Alguien ha visto antes estos tanques?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_10"
msgid "All units, load APDS! We have to destroy them!"
msgstr "¡A todas las unidades, carguen APDS! ¡Tenemos que destruirlos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_12"
msgid "I got one of them! Not as invincible as they look!"
msgstr "¡He conseguido uno! ¡No son tan invencibles como parecen!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/part03_13"
msgid "The second one is burning! Hell yes, we did it, men!"
msgstr "¡El segundo está ardiendo! ¡Sí, lo hemos conseguido, chicos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/cutscene/outro_01"
msgid ""
"Just look at this thing… 150mm armor at least… We got really lucky taking it "
"down…"
msgstr ""
"Solo hay que ver esto... Un blindaje de al menos 150 mm... Tuvimos mucha "
"suerte al derribarlo..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/cutscene/outro_02"
msgid ""
"I’m wondering how many of these Jerry has left. Let’s hope we don’t meet any "
"more of them on our way."
msgstr ""
"Me pregunto cuántos de estos le quedan a Jerry. Esperemos no encontrarnos "
"con más por el camino."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/narrator/secret_infantry"
msgid "So… Should the tank crews take a nap or something?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces... ¿deberían los tripulantes del tanque echarse una siesta o algo "
"así?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/hint_doctrine_unit"
msgid ""
"A new <c(B29557)>doctrine</c> unit is available at the reinforcements tab."
msgstr ""
"Hay una nueva unidad de la doctrina « <c(B29557)>» (Ataque de infantería "
"ligera)</c> disponible en la pestaña «Reinforcements» (Refuerzos)."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/gameover_units_lost"
msgid "You've lost all of your units."
msgstr "Has perdido todas tus unidades."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/reinf_menu_allround"
msgid "<c(B29557)>[All-Round]</c> Forces"
msgstr "<c(B29557)></c> as de las Fuerzas Armadas"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/reinf_menu_offensive"
msgid "<c(B29557)>[Offensive]</c> Forces"
msgstr "<c(B29557)>Fuerzas [ofensivas]</c> "

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/reinf_menu_defensive"
msgid "<c(B29557)>[Defensive]</c> Forces"
msgstr "<c(B29557)>Fuerzas defensivas de la</c> "

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/reinf_menu_irregular"
msgid "<c(B29557)>[Irregular]</c> Forces"
msgstr "<c(B29557)>[Irregular] Fuerzas de la</c> "

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/task01_flank"
msgid "Break through the right Flank to receive Reinforcements"
msgstr "Rompe el flanco derecho para recibir refuerzos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/task02_trench"
msgid "Assist allied Tanks to secure the First Line of Defense"
msgstr "Ayudar a los tanques aliados a asegurar la primera línea de defensa."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/task03_north"
msgid "Secure the northern Part of Cagny and complete the Doctrine Objective"
msgstr "Asegura la parte norte de Cagny y completa el objetivo de la doctrina."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_18_caen_goodwood/ui/task04_allround"
msgid ""
"<c(B29557)>[All-Round Doctrine]</c> Eliminate enemy Infantry covered in "
"Buildings using the Churchill AVRE"
msgstr ""
"<c(B29557)>[Doctrina integral]</c> Elimina la infantería enemiga protegida "
"por edificios utilizando el Churchill AVRE."

